WEBVTT

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.230
Good morning!

00:00:09.230 --> 00:00:11.510
You're looking fired up today.

00:00:11.510 --> 00:00:14.010
Has your next race been settled on yet?

00:00:14.010 --> 00:00:16.600
Well, I'm hoping to run
in the Takarazuka Kinen.

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.370
If I get chosen, anyway.

00:00:18.370 --> 00:00:21.210
The Takarazuka, huh... y'know, Grass-chan—

00:00:21.570 --> 00:00:22.760
Yes?

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:23.750
Pardon me.

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:26.020
Kitasan Black, may I have a word?

00:00:26.020 --> 00:00:26.960
S-Sure!

00:00:27.310 --> 00:00:30.500
I know it's early, but I'd like you
to come to the student council room.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:38.074
