00:02:03.490 --> 00:02:06.980
Episode 10
\hFestival

00:02:04.970 --> 00:02:06.980
You want me to head up a committee?!

00:02:06.980 --> 00:02:08.950
Right. Would you be willing?

00:02:08.950 --> 00:02:11.550
But, well, why me?

00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:14.970
This is a new joint event being
held by the town and the school

00:02:14.970 --> 00:02:16.940
in order to strengthen
relations between both.

00:02:16.940 --> 00:02:22.030
Tracen Academy-Regional
Joint Event

00:02:17.590 --> 00:02:21.730
And as this year's outstanding
horse girl, you're being called up.

00:02:22.700 --> 00:02:27.270
Besides, I've heard you're considered
something of a festival girl.

00:02:27.270 --> 00:02:28.830
W-Well, yeah...

00:02:29.150 --> 00:02:31.870
That's what this will essentially be,

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:35.590
and given your relationship with
the locals, you're a natural fit.

00:02:36.220 --> 00:02:37.620
A festival...

00:02:38.050 --> 00:02:41.240
Yes. We would like you to make a success.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:41.930
How about it?

00:02:43.380 --> 00:02:44.630
It's a festival, then!

00:02:44.630 --> 00:02:47.230
Understood! I'll do my best!

00:02:53.690 --> 00:02:56.650
Tracen Academy-Regional Joint Event

00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:08.540
Photo Stand-In
Panel

00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:08.540
Go right ahead

00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:08.540
I'll take
you on!!!

00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:08.540
H
I
S
H
I

00:03:08.540 --> 00:03:10.790
Kochi & Iwate Products

00:03:10.790 --> 00:03:13.290
Staff

00:03:13.290 --> 00:03:15.910
Okay! As the head of the committee
in charge of this event,

00:03:15.910 --> 00:03:17.820
I'm gonna make it a good one!

00:03:18.860 --> 00:03:20.670
Good morning!

00:03:20.950 --> 00:03:23.860
Hey, Kita-chan! Thanks for having me today!

00:03:23.860 --> 00:03:25.790
Well, thanks for coming!

00:03:25.790 --> 00:03:27.530
We're glad to have you.

00:03:27.530 --> 00:03:31.290
Feels strange, selling my
wares at the school.

00:03:31.290 --> 00:03:34.640
I do like how it makes the event feel
like everyone is pitching in for it.

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.270
Yeah! I hope you all have a good time.

00:03:37.620 --> 00:03:39.020
See you around!

00:03:39.020 --> 00:03:40.720
Yeah! Good luck out there!

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:41.410
Good luck!

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:42.330
Fight!

00:03:47.130 --> 00:03:48.790
Oh, Kita-chan!

00:03:49.390 --> 00:03:50.600
Teio-san!

00:03:51.290 --> 00:03:53.950
You look so cool!

00:03:54.700 --> 00:03:58.420
I heard the Prez did this before,
so I've always wanted to try it myself.

00:03:58.420 --> 00:04:00.280
You're doing the rounds?

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.240
Yeah!

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:04.430
Sorry I haven't been able to
help out with Spica's offering.

00:04:04.430 --> 00:04:06.050
There's no helping that,

00:04:06.050 --> 00:04:08.950
since you're the head of the
committee for putting the event on.

00:04:08.950 --> 00:04:11.830
Leave this to us, and focus
on what you're doing!

00:04:11.830 --> 00:04:14.190
You can come by later for
tea if you have time.

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:15.810
Thanks so much!

00:04:15.810 --> 00:04:17.550
We'll have the tea waiting for you.

00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:18.650
Golshi-san!

00:04:19.810 --> 00:04:21.230
Baa!

00:04:21.230 --> 00:04:22.190
You're a sheep?

00:04:22.190 --> 00:04:24.020
Would you get changed already?!

00:04:24.020 --> 00:04:25.920
Do you understand what we're doing here?!

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:26.570
Stuff it!

00:04:26.870 --> 00:04:30.410
This works for me! Sheep serve people, too!

00:04:30.410 --> 00:04:32.430
What are you talking about?!

00:04:33.410 --> 00:04:35.170
Tracen Academy Regional Joint Event
Route for Making the Rounds
Visit the stalls (in front of the goddess statue)
- Say hello to the folks from the shopping district
\h\hCheck out the interior exhibits!!
- Check in with everyone at Spica
- See Dia-chan and Grand-chan

00:04:34.170 --> 00:04:36.550
Next is...

00:04:36.550 --> 00:04:38.880
Welcome! Welcome!

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:41.850
Would you like to drop in
on the Satono Maid Café?

00:04:41.850 --> 00:04:43.020
Dia-chan...

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:44.790
Kita-chan!

00:04:45.300 --> 00:04:48.180
Dia-chan, you look so cute!
You too, Crown-chan!

00:04:48.180 --> 00:04:50.430
And the Capella trainer...

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:52.300
looks the same as usual!

00:04:52.300 --> 00:04:54.600
Good work on the committee.

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:58.180
Hey, Kitasan, you're running
in the Takarazuka, right?

00:04:58.180 --> 00:05:01.690
You might have me beat in the vote,
but I'm gonna win the race!

00:05:01.940 --> 00:05:04.950
Nope! I don't intend on losing.

00:05:04.950 --> 00:05:07.470
I'll be rooting for you both.

00:05:07.470 --> 00:05:09.740
Are you not entering, Dia-chan?

00:05:09.740 --> 00:05:12.910
Diamond-san is going to be
taking some time to rest.

00:05:12.910 --> 00:05:14.960
I've thought about it a lot...

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:18.000
And I'm going to put everything
I have into the fall.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.210
Heading toward the Prix
de l'Arc de Triomphe.

00:05:20.590 --> 00:05:21.850
Dia-chan...

00:05:22.750 --> 00:05:23.960
I see.

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:26.650
Well, I need to keep doing my rounds!

00:05:26.650 --> 00:05:27.590
Okay.

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:29.320
Good luck!

00:05:34.310 --> 00:05:37.310
Hit him in the navel and
get a prize!!

00:05:40.830 --> 00:05:43.030
Target Challenge

00:05:46.710 --> 00:05:47.610
Wh-What the?!

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:48.970
Yes!

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:52.520
You really got me!

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:53.170
Here you are.

00:05:53.170 --> 00:05:53.990
Thanks.

00:05:54.840 --> 00:05:56.120
Here.

00:05:57.610 --> 00:06:00.260
Thank you! Yay!

00:06:00.260 --> 00:06:01.880
You've gotten better.

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:06.970
Well, I can't afford to
stay the same forever.

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:12.350
Target Challenge

00:06:06.970 --> 00:06:10.540
Just goes to show why you were third
place in the Takarazuka Kinen vote!

00:06:10.540 --> 00:06:12.350
But third place...

00:06:13.570 --> 00:06:15.220
Third place... again.

00:06:19.770 --> 00:06:22.020
Die-Cutting

00:06:32.970 --> 00:06:34.170
Dura-chan!

00:06:34.970 --> 00:06:36.430
Kitasan Black.

00:06:36.430 --> 00:06:39.240
That was a close one. You almost had it.

00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:41.710
It's harder than it seems.

00:06:41.920 --> 00:06:44.150
So, are you having a good time?

00:06:44.150 --> 00:06:48.840
Yeah. It's been a good change
of pace from my usual rehab.

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:52.440
I heard you were heading up
the committee. How's that been?

00:06:52.440 --> 00:06:54.260
Yep! It's been fun!

00:06:54.260 --> 00:06:58.800
Everyone seems so happy,
which helps me feel good too!

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:00.520
I see...

00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:03.050
I suppose you created this scene.

00:07:03.910 --> 00:07:06.020
Aw, come on, it wasn't all me!

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:09.780
But you can do even more.

00:07:11.740 --> 00:07:14.500
One day, I'll do just as much...

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:18.730
No, I will create a scene even more
memorable than what you have

00:07:19.170 --> 00:07:21.250
when I win the Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:25.830
Your dream hasn't changed
at all, huh, Dura-chan?

00:07:25.830 --> 00:07:26.880
It hasn't.

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:33.890
I'll prove I'm strongest, and I will have
all of Japan in a frenzy of excitement.

00:07:36.350 --> 00:07:37.880
All of Japan, huh?

00:07:43.370 --> 00:07:45.090
Then, if you win it...

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:50.120
Everyone in Japan will be laughing,
happy, and making a huge fuss.

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:54.080
That's the kind of race the Prix
de l'Arc de Triomphe is, huh?

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:55.320
Of course.

00:07:55.320 --> 00:07:57.600
It's fair to say it'd be
a historic achievement.

00:07:58.200 --> 00:07:59.620
I see.

00:08:00.340 --> 00:08:03.020
A scene even bigger than this...

00:08:05.010 --> 00:08:07.130
Festival committee head Kitasan Black-san,

00:08:07.130 --> 00:08:09.250
please head to the event operations
tent as soon as possible.

00:08:09.250 --> 00:08:12.010
I've gotta go! Seeya, Dura-chan!

00:08:12.010 --> 00:08:13.830
I hope you have a lot of fun today!

00:08:13.830 --> 00:08:14.970
Right.

